        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Freedom from Regulations Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill requires independent regulatory agencies to comply with the requirements applicable to regulatory actions by other federal agencies, including the rulemaking process under the Administrative Procedure Act.</p>]]></text>
